name: BUBBLEZ#000 - Bubble.bbl
description:
This is the primordial token of the "BUBBLEZ" collection, and insignia of the #BubbleBuddiez. As the origin of all bubblez, it can spawn an unlimited supply, and it will never pop.

Holding at least one edition of this token automatically makes you a #BubbleBuddy!
#BubbleBuddiez will participate of airdrops, rafflez and giveaways, and each edition you own counts as chance of winning. More bubblez = more chances.

After the initial 24hs primary sale, the only way of acquiring "Bubble.bbl" will be via airdrop rewards sent to any person who engages with the project:

-Won an auction? Bubble.
-Lost an auction? Bubble.
-Sold a bubble on secondary? Bubble.
-Plenty of giveaways will take place too.

Anyone can be a #BubbleBuddy, so I hope to see you bubblying soon!

#BUBBLEZ
